  <entry>
    <title>Unity中的Object和object</title>
    <link href="https://github.com/Sheherezade/Sheherezade.github.io/2021/10/24/20211024/"/>
    <id>https://github.com/Sheherezade/Sheherezade.github.io/2021/10/24/20211024/</id>
    <published>2021-10-24T14:28:58.909Z</published>
    <updated>2021-10-24T14:31:55.780Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&emsp;&emsp;最近在学习反射的时候，去找所谓的<code>Type</code>,在<code>UnityEngine</code>的<code>Object</code>中找了半天没找到，最后在<code>System.Object</code>下面发现了<code>GetType</code>()的方法，索性研究一下。</p><hr><p>先来一些基本概念</p><ul><li>在C#中任何一个<code>class</code>类即使不写<code>class XXX:System.Object</code> 也会被默认继承<code>System.Object</code></li><li><code>object</code>关键字与<code>System.Object</code>等价 应该是c++层有定义</li></ul><hr><p>查阅资料的时候发现，很多文章里都有这样一个有趣的实验</p><ol><li><p>首先自己去定义一个最精简的mono类</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>UnityEngine;</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public class CustomMono : MonoBehaviour&#123; &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在场景中创建一个空物体，接着自己再创建一个用来测试逻辑的脚本<code>TestScript</code></p></li><li><p> 进行测试</p><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Awake</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">   &#123;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="built_in">bool</span> res_unity = GetComponent&lt;Light&gt;() == <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="built_in">bool</span> res_custom = GetComponent&lt;CustomMono&gt;() == <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       Debug.Log(<span class="string">$&quot;<span class="subst">&#123;res_unity&#125;</span>-----<span class="subst">&#123;res_custom&#125;</span>&quot;</span>);<span class="comment">//true-----true</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">       res_unity = (<span class="built_in">object</span>)GetComponent&lt;Light&gt;() == <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       res_custom = (<span class="built_in">object</span>)GetComponent&lt;CustomMono&gt;() == <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       Debug.Log(<span class="string">$&quot;<span class="subst">&#123;res_unity&#125;</span>-----<span class="subst">&#123;res_custom&#125;</span>&quot;</span>);<span class="comment">//false-----true</span></span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&emsp;&emsp;可以看到unity自带的系统组件和我们自己编写的mono组件出现了不同的情况</p></li><li><p>这时候试下<code>is</code>关键字</p><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Debug.Log(GetComponent&lt;Light&gt;() <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="literal">null</span>);<span class="comment">//false</span></span><br><span class="line">   Debug.Log(GetComponent&lt;CustomMono&gt;() <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="literal">null</span>);<span class="comment">//true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><ul><li>可以看出来当使用<code>GetComponent</code>获取unity<font color=#ff0000><strong>内置</strong></font>的系统组件时，永远不会返回null</li><li>unity内部针对系统组件的*==* 和 <em>!=</em> 运算符进行了重载，来得到看上去正确的结果，所以当我们使用<em>is</em>关键字的时候，它就原形毕露了!</li><li>使用 <em>??</em> 和 <em>?.</em> 语法糖时，也需要注意不要再unity的系统组件上使用，不然当你尝试<br>  <code>GetComponent&lt;Light&gt;()?.gameObject</code>会出现bug</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&amp;emsp;&amp;emsp;最近在学习反射的时候，去找所谓的&lt;code&gt;Type&lt;/code&gt;,在&lt;code&gt;UnityEngine&lt;/code&gt;的&lt;code&gt;Object&lt;/code&gt;中找了半天没找到，最后在&lt;code&gt;System.Object&lt;/code&gt;下面发现了&lt;co</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
